{"tid":862584,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"樓市好消息》發展商惜售高質單位 周末一手成交110宗","createTime":"2018-10-15T02:44:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-15T04:22:39.000Z","uid":13663,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5ba3449e48618c9d48b9f981eacd1ab1b83c1889","tid":862584,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T02:44:34.000Z","msg":"周末一手成交110宗 LP6推491伙僅沽98伙<br />\n關閉<br />\n2018/10/15 09:49 留言    沽空   股價<br />\n <br />\n政府公布《施政報告》後首個周末(10月13至14日)，新盤市場錄約110宗成交，按周回落50%，當中南豐將軍澳LP6第4輪開售491伙，但受市況波動影響，兩日僅沽出約98伙；此外，九建(<a href=\"http://00034.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00034.HK&d=Pu874G7vRu0OUCz98EcujQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=172bb356\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00034.HK</a>)  -0.050 (-0.620%)    沽空 $18.47萬; 比率 5.764%   油塘海傲灣亦錄成交。<br />\n<br />\n二手方面，中原地產十大屋苑周末錄得4宗成交，按周持平；美聯物業十大藍籌屋苑周末錄得1宗成交，按周跌50%；利嘉閣地產十大指標屋苑周末錄3宗二手買賣個案，按周升50%；香港置業十大主要藍籌屋苑周末則錄得1宗成交，按周跌逾六成。(ac/lf)(報價延遲最少十五分鐘。沽空資料截至 2018-10-12 16:25。)"},{"pid":"23debddf0ce31f9490b944e3dec252c6aa677a56","tid":862584,"uid":42921,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T02:45:28.000Z","msg":"大利好消息，Hold住唔買，出年加價一倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5262fa946b83a97c79b3f69d474fb335159e7f0","tid":862584,"uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"23debddf0ce31f9490b944e3dec252c6aa677a56","tid":862584,"uid":42921,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T02:45:28.000Z","msg":"大利好消息，Hold住唔買，出年加價一倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T02:48:02.000Z","msg":"Hold十年<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">估值</span>升n倍 華懋就係好既例子"},{"pid":"7